The Ansible playbook contained within this directory will build cloudscheduler
version 2 in a real or Virtual Machine (VM) which has the following characteristics:

   o At least 2 cores
   o At least 4 GiB of memory.
   o A root block device with CentOS 7 installed; at least 50 GiB is recommeded.
   o A storage block device; At least 50GiB is recommended.

Once CentOS has been installed, The two files, "csv2-sa-secrets.yaml" and
"csv2-sa-vars.yaml" should be modified to contain appropriate values for the 
deployment and then the playbook can be run with the following command:

   ansible-playbook -e addenda=addenda -i inventory csv2-sa.yaml
